I chose to buy this one primarily because all of the films in the set were ones I had previously enjoyed. They all have that 'spark' that is needed that moves us and interests enough to want to watch again.  For me, the biggest value is having a second chance to watch these movies on discs that have not been environmentally challenged:)  They are new discs without physical flaws and the prices for the ability to re-watch great actors is great.
Great condition and very good movies!

This was a defective product.  Unfortunately, I didn't try to match any of the movies on it until over a month had gone by.  I could open and see all of the movies except House of the Spirits.  I do not know if all the copies being sold are like that, but anyone buying it should watch it right away to see if they need to return it.
Not all great movies, but all worth a view.
